snippet.title: Diana plays with Disney Princess Rapunzel Doll
snippet.description:
Diana has a new toys - Disney Princess Rapunzel Doll with a horse. Diana is playing with a horse and does not allow anyone to play with her. But it's not good to be greedy ... Therefore, something incredible happens to a toy horse!
